1166
01:20:36.793 --> 01:20:38.192  X1:206 X2:509 Y1:496 Y2:530
Now. give me the gun.

1167
01:20:38.433 --> 01:20:40.025  X1:177 X2:536 Y1:448 Y2:524
You don't wanna go to jail
in Mexico.

1168
01:20:40.233 --> 01:20:44.306  X1:118 X2:598 Y1:448 Y2:530
Nobody wanna go to jail in Mexico.
They put burritos in your ass.

1169
01:20:44.513 --> 01:20:45.389  X1:299 X2:414 Y1:496 Y2:530
Shut up!

1170
01:20:45.593 --> 01:20:48.391  X1:126 X2:590 Y1:448 Y2:524
Come on. Deke. Give me the gun.
Come on!

1171
01:20:48.593 --> 01:20:52.381  X1:176 X2:538 Y1:448 Y2:530
They think I'm a cop!
They think I'm a cop. man!

1172
01:20:52.633 --> 01:20:54.510  X1:211 X2:505 Y1:496 Y2:530
I can help you. okay?

1173
01:20:54.753 --> 01:20:57.551  X1:178 X2:536 Y1:448 Y2:530
You don't wanna die here.
Now give that up.

1174
01:20:57.753 --> 01:21:00.631  X1:137 X2:578 Y1:448 Y2:530
If you screw me. I swear to God.
I'll come back for you.

1175
01:21:00.833 --> 01:21:02.425  X1:204 X2:510 Y1:496 Y2:530
I'll come back for you!

1176
01:21:02.713 --> 01:21:03.748  X1:241 X2:473 Y1:496 Y2:530
Give me the gun!

1177
01:21:06.233 --> 01:21:08.542  X1:185 X2:530 Y1:448 Y2:530
There you go.
Let me get that from you.

1178
01:21:08.913 --> 01:21:10.790  X1:223 X2:492 Y1:496 Y2:530
