1181
01:21:26.393 --> 01:21:27.428  X1:276 X2:439 Y1:496 Y2:530
Holy Christ!

1182
01:21:31.233 --> 01:21:32.109  X1:243 X2:471 Y1:496 Y2:524
That's for Eddie.

1183
01:21:37.753 --> 01:21:39.152  X1:226 X2:487 Y1:496 Y2:524
You son of a bitch!

1184
01:21:39.353 --> 01:21:40.752  X1:243 X2:472 Y1:496 Y2:524
Come back here!

1185
01:21:41.033 --> 01:21:42.102  X1:226 X2:487 Y1:496 Y2:524
You son of a bitch!

1186
01:21:42.953 --> 01:21:44.227  X1:257 X2:457 Y1:496 Y2:530
Miles. you die!

1187
01:22:17.553 --> 01:22:18.781  X1:263 X2:452 Y1:496 Y2:530
You all right?

1188
01:22:19.633 --> 01:22:21.908  X1:119 X2:598 Y1:496 Y2:530
I needed a vacation anyway. right?

1189
01:22:23.553 --> 01:22:26.147  X1:159 X2:554 Y1:448 Y2:524
The FBI needs to talk to you.
Detective Malone.

1190
01:22:30.353 --> 01:22:33.902  X1:136 X2:580 Y1:448 Y2:524
Peterson. regional director. FBl.
We need to talk.

1191
01:22:34.113 --> 01:22:36.149  X1:171 X2:542 Y1:496 Y2:524
Wait a minute. Slow down.

1192
01:22:36.353 --> 01:22:38.150  X1:113 X2:603 Y1:496 Y2:529
No. lieutenant. I will not slow down.

1193
01:22:38.433 --> 01:22:40.469  X1:178 X2:538 Y1:496 Y2:530
Is this man one of yours...

1194
01:22:41.233 --> 01:22:42.552  X1:295 X2:421 Y1:496 Y2:524
...or not?

1195
01:22:44.313 --> 01:22:45.792  X1:197 X2:516 Y1:496 Y2:530
You bet your ass he is.

1196
01:22:46.633 --> 01:22:49.352  X1:193 X2:521 Y1:448 Y2:530
Well. I'm gonna find out
what happened here...

1197
01:22:49.713 --> 01:22:54.628  X1:102 X2:614 Y1:448 Y2:530
