1202
01:23:13.753 --> 01:23:15.823  X1:194 X2:521 Y1:448 Y2:530
It's time that you
gave us an explanation.

1203
01:23:20.793 --> 01:23:22.226  X1:260 X2:454 Y1:496 Y2:524
I'm a federale.

1204
01:23:22.433 --> 01:23:23.229  X1:277 X2:437 Y1:496 Y2:524
A federale?

1205
01:23:24.553 --> 01:23:26.987  X1:188 X2:527 Y1:448 Y2:530
