What do you see?

1206
01:23:27.233 --> 01:23:30.384  X1:202 X2:514 Y1:448 Y2:530
That is the Democratic
Republic of Mexico.

1207
01:23:30.593 --> 01:23:31.389  X1:242 X2:472 Y1:496 Y2:524
You're Mexican?

1208
01:23:31.593 --> 01:23:34.027  X1:154 X2:560 Y1:448 Y2:530
That's right.
On my mother's father's side.

1209
01:23:34.233 --> 01:23:35.188  X1:278 X2:438 Y1:496 Y2:524
I can see it.

1210
01:23:35.393 --> 01:23:36.621  X1:218 X2:498 Y1:496 Y2:530
Glacias. Thank you.

1211
01:23:36.833 --> 01:23:39.142  X1:181 X2:534 Y1:448 Y2:530
