1213
01:23:41.033 --> 01:23:41.829  X1:279 X2:436 Y1:496 Y2:524
Your what?

1214
01:23:42.033 --> 01:23:43.386  X1:234 X2:480 Y1:496 Y2:530
My federale-hood!

1215
01:23:44.633 --> 01:23:46.669  X1:081 X2:636 Y1:496 Y2:530
