1220
01:23:55.233 --> 01:23:58.225  X1:162 X2:554 Y1:448 Y2:524
If you'll excuse me.
I have to cross this border...

1221
01:23:58.433 --> 01:24:01.425  X1:101 X2:613 Y1:448 Y2:530
...and school some of my compadres.
you know...

1222
01:24:01.633 --> 01:24:05.148  X1:132 X2:583 Y1:448 Y2:530
