So y'all stay up. Be cool.

1223
01:24:13.113 --> 01:24:16.662  X1:150 X2:565 Y1:448 Y2:530
What's happening?
Hook a brother up with a taco!

1224
01:24:16.873 --> 01:24:18.386  X1:290 X2:423 Y1:496 Y2:524
A burrito!

1225
01:24:22.033 --> 01:24:26.151  X1:108 X2:606 Y1:448 Y2:530
I can't believe so much bad shit
can happen on such a beautiful day.

1226
01:24:30.633 --> 01:24:32.146  X1:273 X2:442 Y1:496 Y2:529
Yeah. what?

1227
