I think your Spanish is a little rusty.

1228
01:24:34.433 --> 01:24:37.743  X1:141 X2:573 Y1:448 Y2:530
You just told those men
you got a big cat in your pants.

1229
01:24:41.433 --> 01:24:44.630  X1:162 X2:552 Y1:448 Y2:524
