in a police building. what would I do?

1236
01:25:03.713 --> 01:25:05.226  X1:183 X2:531 Y1:496 Y2:530
So I thought like a crook.

1237
01:25:05.553 --> 01:25:07.032  X1:269 X2:447 Y1:496 Y2:530
Is that right?

1238
01:25:07.753 --> 01:25:08.868  X1:226 X2:490 Y1:496 Y2:524
