1249
01:25:40.153 --> 01:25:43.509  X1:120 X2:597 Y1:448 Y2:530
If I'm across the border and you're
over there. there's no way you--

1250
01:25:47.393 --> 01:25:49.304  X1:171 X2:544 Y1:496 Y2:530
