1253
01:25:58.833 --> 01:25:59.629  X1:263 X2:454 Y1:496 Y2:524
Is it like that?

1254
01:25:59.993 --> 01:26:01.392  X1:222 X2:491 Y1:496 Y2:524
Yeah. It's like that.

1255
01:26:12.033 --> 01:26:14.149  X1:181 X2:534 Y1:496 Y2:530
Right there. Jurisdiction.

1256
01:26:17.553 --> 01:26:18.429  X1:303 X2:411 Y1:496 Y2:524
Thanks.

1257
01:26:21.633 --> 01:26:23.385  X1:234 X2:482 Y1:496 Y2:524
Viva Las Mexico...

1258
